name: Impossible Tracks 3: Extreme
description:
The impossible race tracks have a long list of the mega ramp with addition of the ramp stunts of the stunt racing games. The player of the stunt car games has a chance to polish his impossible track driving during this impossible challenge of the impossible track car game
Features:
Splendid 3D graphics
Elevated stunts
Mid-air stunts
High quality sounds
Best collection of cars
